name: PhiNesse Eyebrow Pen 3-in-1 3pcs
short_description: PhiNesse Eyebrow Pen 3in1 is a full eyebrow beautifying set in just one compact pen. It contains three components crucial for creating flawless eyebrow look.
long_description: -eyebrow pencil to outline the brow shape and to fill in the brows-powder brush to add a shading or ombré effect-brow building mascara to set the created look and to add the desired depth and dimension of the brows The set contains three pens in the following shades : 1 light brown 2 medium brown 3 dark brown all three shades in a set to achieve an effect of natural eyebrows for different looks and skin tones.
